Interface TracedDynamicField<T extends Serializable>

Type Parameters:
T - bounded type must be Serializable
All Superinterfaces:
Serializable
All Known Subinterfaces:
DynamicField<T>, LabeledDynamicField<T>, UnlockableTracedDynamicField<T>
All Known Implementing Classes:
BaseDynamicField, BaseLabeledDynamicField, BaseTracedDynamicField, BooleanEditableField, DoubleEditableField, FloatEditableField, IntegerEditableField, LongEditableField, StringEditableField, UnlockableTracedDynamicFieldImpl
public interface TracedDynamicField<T extends Serializable> extends Serializable
Represents a field that is computed dynamically by the backend. This is useful for dynamic forms and provide possibility to reset to initialized value.
Author:
Eugen Fischer
